  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 41-58-7, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE LICENSURE QUALIFICATIONS FOR RADIOLOGIST ASSISTANTS; TO AUTHORIZE A RADIOLOGIST ASSISTANT TO COMMUNICATE A PRELIMINARY IMAGE INTERPRETATION REPORT WITH INITIAL OBSERVATIONS TO OTHER CARE PROVIDERS TREATING A PATIENT; TO REQUIRE THAT A RADIOLOGIST PROVIDE FINAL IMAGE INTERPRETATION; TO AUTHORIZE A RADIOLOGIST ASSISTANT TO COMMUNICATE A RADIOLOGIST'S PRELIMINARY OR FINAL IMAGE INTERPRETATION TO OTHER CARE PROVIDERS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
